snippet.title: Darkour - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Darkour is a 2D platformer where darkness is your platform. http://darkourgame.com/

Wishlist on Steam / Play the 40 Level Demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1164860/Darkour/
Also available here: https://bmegana.itch.io/darkour

The game has a planned release date of November 11, 2019 (Veterans Day).

It is being made in Unity by Brian Egana.

Character Art and Animation: Angie Pelina (https://angiepelina.weebly.com/)

Trailer Music: deep sixxx by I Swear to God. (https://soundcloud.com/minimalsystemrecordings/deep-sixxx-mp3)
License: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
